<script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    var flip = 0;
    var mobileMenuIcon = document.getElementById('webyx-elmnt-icon-mobile-menu');
    var menu = document.getElementById('webyx-elmnt-menu');
    var headerListItems = document.querySelectorAll('.webyx-section-header ul li');

    mobileMenuIcon.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
        event.stopPropagation(); // Evita la propagazione dell'evento click al gestore del documento
        var isHidden = menu.style.display === 'none' || menu.style.display === '';
        if (isHidden) {
            openMenu();
        } else {
            closeMenu();
        }
    });
    document.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
        if (menu.style.display !== 'none' && menu.style.display !== '') {
            closeMenu();
        }
    });
    headerListItems.forEach(function(item) {
        item.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
            if (menu.style.display !== 'none' && menu.style.display !== '') {
                event.stopPropagation(); // Evita la propagazione dell'evento click al gestore del documento
                closeMenu();
            }
        });
    });

    function openMenu() {
        menu.style.display = 'block';
        menu.style.height = '0px';
        menu.style.overflow = 'hidden';
        var maxHeight = menu.scrollHeight + 'px';
        menu.style.height = '0px'; // Impostare l'altezza a 0 prima dell'animazione
        setTimeout(function() {
            menu.style.transition = 'height 0.25s';
            menu.style.height = maxHeight;
        }, 10);
    }
    function closeMenu() {
        menu.style.transition = 'height 0.25s';
        menu.style.height = '0px';
        menu.style.overflow = 'hidden';
        menu.addEventListener('transitionend', function() {
            menu.removeAttribute('style');
        }, { once: true });
    }
});

</script>
